#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.166:0.2"
msgid "13. Esanāvagga "
msgstr "13. Searches "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.166:0.3"
msgid "166. Khilasutta "
msgstr "166. Kinds of Barrenness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.57, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.166:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, khilā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three kinds of barrenness. "

msgctxt "sn45.166:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "sn45.166:1.3"
msgid "Rāgo khilo, doso khilo, moho khilo—"
msgstr "Greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.166:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo khilā. "
msgstr "These are the three kinds of barrenness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.166:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇannaṃ khilānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these three kinds of barrenness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.166:1.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

